Privacy Policy
Personal data (usually referred to just as "data" below) will not be processed by us or our SmartConnect app.
Per Art. 4 No. 1 of Regulation (EU) 2016/679, i.e. the General Data Protection Regulation (hereinafter referred to
    as the "GDPR"), "processing" refers to any operation or set of operations such as collection, recording,
    organization, structuring, storage, adaptation, alteration, retrieval, consultation, use, disclosure by
    transmission, dissemination, or otherwise making available, alignment, or combination, restriction, erasure, or
    destruction performed on personal data, whether by automated means or not.